&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in engineering or related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent initiative and interpersonal communications skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize, multi-task, deal with ambiguity, and manage high volume projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Desire to grow professionally and possess an interest in establishing a career in equipment sales&lt;/li&gt;
